              "id": "9813a5e",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "\n<header style=\"padding:160px 5% 100px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(10,22,40,0.92) 0%,rgba(15,52,96,0.85) 60%,rgba(12,207,176,0.12) 100%),url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1466611653911-95081537e5b7?w=1800&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;color:#fff\">\n  <div style=\"font-size:0.8rem;color:#0ccfb0;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px\">Home → Projects</div>\n  <h1 style=\"font-size:clamp(2rem,4.5vw,3.4rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-0.02em;max-width:900px;margin-bottom:20px\">Sustainability Projects <span style='color:#0ccfb0'>Delivered Worldwide</span></h1>\n  <p style=\"font-size:1.1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.72);line-height:1.7;max-width:640px\">Innovative solutions for zero-emission energy, efficient infrastructure, advanced water treatment, hydrogen and ammonia production, and power grid enhancements for environmental protection.</p>\n</header>"
